citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1240 on 20 JUN 23.
The licensee was not home, but I was able to speak with her by phone. She stated she would not be able to return for
several hours and was unavailable for inspection.
End Section
